  m_text: "Why Register? \nSo we can personalise and optimise your experience. Specifically\n1.
    You will only be able to access some of the behaviour change areas, since we
    need specific information about you to tailor your journey\n2.  Retrieve your
    settings on any device\n3. Each time you tell Master Change a little more about
    yourself, you will earn more Riros to spend within the app\n4. By registering
    you are taking the first step in commiting to make the changes you wish to see
    in your life\n\n"
